WEBVTT

00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:14.900
♪I look at you, like at another me♪

00:00:16.780 --> 00:00:24.540
♪My heart is locked up, never free♪

00:00:25.260 --> 00:00:34.420
♪Sometimes I go with it, spinning like a top♪

00:00:35.060 --> 00:00:44.300
♪No one to tell my secrets to, so I stay silent♪

00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:54.620
♪Loud is the echo I buried deep♪

00:00:57.300 --> 00:01:03.700
♪How I crave a single reply♪

00:01:04.060 --> 00:01:08.660
♪Lonely souls are sand in the wind♪

00:01:09.260 --> 00:01:13.620
♪With nowhere to settle♪

00:01:13.980 --> 00:01:18.460
♪Broken all over, yet my heart won't give♪

00:01:19.020 --> 00:01:24.220
♪Like a flower blooming in a crack of stone♪

00:01:24.420 --> 00:01:28.980
[Loving Strangers]

00:01:29.020 --> 00:01:33.940
[Episode 5]

00:01:34.700 --> 00:01:39.140
[Sen'an Pharma]

00:01:41.160 --> 00:01:42.690
You can't do this.

00:01:43.120 --> 00:01:44.130
Before I placed the order,

00:01:44.150 --> 00:01:45.330
I checked with customer service

00:01:45.350 --> 00:01:46.980
about whether you could issue an invoice.

00:01:47.400 --> 00:01:48.410
They said you could,

00:01:48.410 --> 00:01:49.770
so I bought it from you.

00:01:50.110 --> 00:01:50.930
I don't care.

00:01:51.190 --> 00:01:52.050
What's wrong with the gift card?

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:53.770
Isn't a gift card bought with real money?

00:01:53.830 --> 00:01:55.330
That's your problem.

00:01:56.080 --> 00:01:56.410
Fine.

00:01:56.510 --> 00:01:57.620
Then wait for my complaint.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:02.980
What's wrong?

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:05.820
Online shops just bully customers now.

00:02:06.230 --> 00:02:07.770
I clearly told them I needed an invoice,

00:02:07.800 --> 00:02:08.940
then after I paid, they said they couldn't issue it.

00:02:10.530 --> 00:02:11.450
Why can't they?

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:12.640
I paid with our company's

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:14.170
employee welfare gift card.

00:02:14.420 --> 00:02:15.010
They said

00:02:15.030 --> 00:02:16.130
when our company bought the cards,

00:02:16.130 --> 00:02:17.570
they had already issued an invoice,

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:18.980
and they can't issue it twice.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.890
Then at least tell me upfront!

00:02:21.430 --> 00:02:22.170
If they don't reply by tomorrow,

00:02:22.240 --> 00:02:23.500
I'll file a complaint with the Consumers' Association.

00:02:26.310 --> 00:02:26.980
Will that help?

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:28.340
If you complain to the Consumers' Association,

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:29.820
the seller has to respond.

00:02:30.080 --> 00:02:31.010
At least, they need to provide proof

00:02:31.030 --> 00:02:32.340
that an invoice was already issued,

00:02:32.470 --> 00:02:33.570
plus the relevant laws and rules,

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:34.660
all in writing.

00:02:43.180 --> 00:02:45.900
[Jiang Jiaqi]

00:02:49.470 --> 00:02:49.890
Hello?

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:51.290
Mr. Pang, is now a good time?

00:02:51.520 --> 00:02:52.380
I need to talk to you.

00:02:53.910 --> 00:02:54.480
Okay.

00:02:54.980 --> 00:02:55.680
Roof, then.

00:02:56.070 --> 00:02:56.570
Sure.

00:02:57.580 --> 00:02:58.130
Boss,

00:02:59.210 --> 00:03:00.500
can you sign this for me?

00:03:05.870 --> 00:03:06.410
Okay.

00:03:09.190 --> 00:03:09.820
I'm heading out.

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:10.500
Okay.

00:03:12.460 --> 00:03:15.380
[Zhe]

00:03:20.100 --> 00:03:21.730
Dial the number I sent you.

00:03:21.880 --> 00:03:22.500
Keep dialing.

00:03:43.070 --> 00:03:44.220
Your phone.

00:03:45.780 --> 00:03:46.660
It's been ringing nonstop.

00:03:54.030 --> 00:03:54.660
Hello?

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:55.690
Hello, sir.

00:03:55.750 --> 00:03:57.820
[Jiang]
Are you the owner of car 7463?

00:03:58.150 --> 00:03:59.660
Could you come down and move it?

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:00.690
You dialed the wrong number.

00:04:13.150 --> 00:04:14.340
Any news from the e-commerce platform?

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:17.340
It's tougher than I thought.

00:04:18.830 --> 00:04:19.850
I heard earlier,

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:21.410
they leaked

00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:22.460
customer info

00:04:22.750 --> 00:04:23.730
and got exposed online.

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:25.580
Unless it's for the police and courts,

00:04:26.070 --> 00:04:26.850
they won't share anything

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:28.020
with outsiders.

00:04:29.430 --> 00:04:30.780
I'm asking a friend

00:04:31.270 --> 00:04:31.930
to see

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:33.980
if we can reach their top people.

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:36.540
I have an idea.

00:04:37.270 --> 00:04:38.370
It might be worth a try.

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:42.850
Tell me.

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:45.050
Those 200k e-commerce gift cards

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:46.340
were probably

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:47.730
paid for by some company,

00:04:48.750 --> 00:04:49.610
so it definitely involves

00:04:49.630 --> 00:04:50.610
how they booked it.

00:04:51.070 --> 00:04:52.140
There should be an invoice.

00:04:52.390 --> 00:04:53.340
Isn't that the same

00:04:53.360 --> 00:04:54.580
as checking who bought them?

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:56.810
If we use

00:04:56.830 --> 00:04:58.340
those cards to shop,

00:04:58.950 --> 00:04:59.730
then ask them

00:04:59.750 --> 00:05:00.610
to issue an invoice too?

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:03.140
Spell it out.

00:05:04.480 --> 00:05:05.930
Invoices can't be issued twice.

00:05:06.190 --> 00:05:06.730
Exactly.

00:05:07.480 --> 00:05:08.700
Then we can file a complaint

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:10.220
and ask for proof

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:11.610
that an invoice was already issued.

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:15.540
That way, we'll know

00:05:15.560 --> 00:05:16.580
the company's name.

00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:18.250
But all of this needs

00:05:18.270 --> 00:05:19.290
the Inspection Office's help.

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:21.020
They have to agree

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:22.540
to let us use those cards.

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.980
To trace the bribe source,

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:27.170
they've got no reason to refuse.

00:05:29.310 --> 00:05:30.410
Not bad, kid!

00:05:31.430 --> 00:05:31.900
All right.

00:05:32.750 --> 00:05:34.100
I'll handle it tomorrow morning.

00:05:34.870 --> 00:05:35.810
Once we find proof,

00:05:36.680 --> 00:05:37.930
we can follow the trail

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:38.810
and wipe them out for good.

00:05:40.430 --> 00:05:41.610
I'll prove it to you.

00:05:42.040 --> 00:05:42.810
You picked the right side.

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:45.900
This has nothing to do with sides.

00:05:47.040 --> 00:05:48.250
I just don't want to be smeared

00:05:48.270 --> 00:05:49.100
for no reason.

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:54.730
Jiaqi,

00:05:57.270 --> 00:05:58.540
you're still too naive.

00:06:00.190 --> 00:06:00.810
It's not because

00:06:00.830 --> 00:06:02.490
you want to mess with someone.

00:06:03.390 --> 00:06:04.930
It's so you don't get messed with

00:06:05.190 --> 00:06:06.140
that you have to pick a side.

00:06:07.830 --> 00:06:09.610
The situation's changed again.

00:06:10.020 --> 00:06:11.700
Do you know why the chairman sent me

00:06:12.270 --> 00:06:13.250
to report to the drug regulator?

00:06:14.750 --> 00:06:17.340
SA-0988's

00:06:17.800 --> 00:06:18.580
Phase III trial

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.730
is basically a black hole!

00:06:21.950 --> 00:06:23.020
If the data looks bad,

00:06:23.480 --> 00:06:25.340
we can tweak the trial plan.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.340
But if the data is fake,

00:06:28.310 --> 00:06:30.050
that's a fatal blow.

00:06:31.950 --> 00:06:33.370
This means the chairman

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:34.850
already has personal doubts

00:06:34.950 --> 00:06:35.900
about Gu Chen.

00:06:37.630 --> 00:06:38.290
Currently, the chairman

00:06:38.310 --> 00:06:39.580
is under a ton of pressure.

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:40.930
This time,

00:06:41.750 --> 00:06:42.730
if we can meet

00:06:42.740 --> 00:06:44.220
the regulator's standards,

00:06:44.680 --> 00:06:45.660
then at Sen'an,

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.290
the chairman

00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:48.850
will take us more seriously.

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:51.340
For that,

00:06:51.830 --> 00:06:53.020
we should grab some drinks.

00:06:54.950 --> 00:06:56.290
You can't dodge this one.

00:06:56.750 --> 00:06:57.900
Let's head to Jiangbei,

00:06:58.040 --> 00:06:59.220
eat pork intestines, and drink hard liquor.

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:00.700
Then find a karaoke place

00:07:00.750 --> 00:07:01.610
and belt out a few songs!

00:07:22.390 --> 00:07:23.660
If you still want to stay at this company,

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:26.340
then show me results soon.

00:07:26.920 --> 00:07:27.930
Pang Jian's going to get the gift cards

00:07:27.950 --> 00:07:28.660
from the Inspection Office,

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:29.700
and use the invoices

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:30.780
to trace the company behind them.

00:07:31.560 --> 00:07:32.290
How do you know?

00:07:33.040 --> 00:07:33.900
Believe it or not.

00:07:34.430 --> 00:07:35.100
Right now,

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:36.930
go to the overpass behind the office.

00:08:03.950 --> 00:08:05.020
You picked a good spot.

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:08.460
No one comes here.

00:08:08.510 --> 00:08:09.050
It's safe.

00:08:11.750 --> 00:08:13.140
Can you keep the Inspection Office in check?

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:16.610
As long as Pang Jian doesn't get the cards,

00:08:16.630 --> 00:08:17.490
they can't do anything.

00:08:18.750 --> 00:08:20.220
If I step in and interfere with Inspection Office,

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:22.170
you know what that means.

00:08:22.630 --> 00:08:23.700
It means admitting you did it.

00:08:30.900 --> 00:08:32.600
[Recordings]

00:08:32.600 --> 00:08:33.730
Those 200k e-commerce gift cards

00:08:34.550 --> 00:08:36.300
were probably paid for by some company,

00:08:36.750 --> 00:08:37.730
so it definitely involves

00:08:37.750 --> 00:08:38.530
how they booked it.

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:40.100
There should be an invoice.

00:08:52.550 --> 00:08:53.580
Is this enough

00:08:53.910 --> 00:08:55.100
to save my job?

00:08:59.870 --> 00:09:00.730
This is the first batch.

00:09:03.510 --> 00:09:04.490
Next time, get Pang Jian out.

00:09:06.150 --> 00:09:06.980
You have one night

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.010
to deal with the Inspection Office.

00:09:16.300 --> 00:09:19.900
[Sen'an Pharma]

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:20.700
Hello?

00:09:21.550 --> 00:09:22.700
Is there an invoice for those gift cards?

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:24.700
Yeah.

00:09:28.270 --> 00:09:29.220
Hello?

00:09:30.270 --> 00:09:31.350
- Hello? - Hello, what?

00:09:31.840 --> 00:09:33.100
You got me killed!

00:09:48.700 --> 00:09:51.980
[Mr. Gu]

00:09:56.290 --> 00:09:57.010
Okay. Got it.

00:09:58.460 --> 00:09:59.010
Fine.

00:09:59.270 --> 00:10:00.530
I'll talk to Su Gengsheng.

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:01.580
When he got promoted to director,

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:02.130
I helped him.

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:04.300
He should know which side to stand on.

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:07.060
Thank you!

00:10:07.150 --> 00:10:07.820
Thank you, Mr. Gu!

00:10:24.910 --> 00:10:25.730
Hello, Director Su.

00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:27.300
It's Gu Chen.

00:10:34.870 --> 00:10:35.460
Su Gengsheng,

00:10:35.670 --> 00:10:36.700
stop playing dumb with me.

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:38.460
Why not?

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:39.700
Investigating bribery

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:41.010
is Inspection Office's job.

00:10:41.630 --> 00:10:42.820
Those gift cards are evidence.

00:10:43.320 --> 00:10:44.370
How could we let you take them?

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:45.980
How about this?

00:10:46.870 --> 00:10:48.060
I'll buy a few cards myself,

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:49.010
swap them one-for-one.

00:10:49.080 --> 00:10:49.460
That works, right?

00:10:49.670 --> 00:10:51.460
You want me to sell you

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:52.240
criminal evidence?

00:10:53.870 --> 00:10:55.130
I'm not playing word games with you.

00:10:56.320 --> 00:10:57.130
I'm the Vice GM.

00:10:58.120 --> 00:10:59.530
You have to do what I say.

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:01.370
Sorry, Mr. Pang.

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:02.980
Inspection Office

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.060
has its own way of handling things.

00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:12.820
Su Gengsheng,

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:15.610
so the Vice GM doesn't count,

00:11:16.390 --> 00:11:17.340
but the CEO does,

00:11:17.390 --> 00:11:18.610
am I right?

00:11:20.150 --> 00:11:20.650
Mr. Pang,

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:22.610
I hope you know

00:11:22.630 --> 00:11:23.460
what you're saying.

00:11:27.390 --> 00:11:28.180
I know exactly.

00:12:06.790 --> 00:12:07.300
Boss,

00:12:08.550 --> 00:12:09.460
the hospitals are lined up.

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:15.300
Hey, did you actually

00:12:15.320 --> 00:12:16.420
explain it clearly?

00:12:16.840 --> 00:12:18.180
We have to hit three hospitals today.

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:19.010
No car available.

00:12:20.150 --> 00:12:20.980
Can you stop

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:22.010
spitting out few words at a time?

00:12:22.390 --> 00:12:24.010
Will a full sentence kill you?

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:28.010
Always pulling that sour face.

00:12:28.550 --> 00:12:28.980
What's with the attitude?

00:12:29.270 --> 00:12:29.850
If I were Admin,

00:12:29.850 --> 00:12:30.850
even with a car, I'd still say no.

00:12:31.530 --> 00:12:32.060
Real funny.

00:12:32.120 --> 00:12:32.530
Boss,

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:34.130
want me to ask again?

00:12:34.720 --> 00:12:35.340
Let's just get a cab.

00:12:58.360 --> 00:12:59.820
Didn't the forecast say

00:13:00.080 --> 00:13:01.010
today would warm up?

00:13:01.390 --> 00:13:02.340
The sun's out already.

00:13:02.440 --> 00:13:03.730
So why's it still freezing?

00:13:04.120 --> 00:13:05.300
Since when did the forecast

00:13:05.320 --> 00:13:06.250
have to be right?

00:13:06.550 --> 00:13:07.300
And since when

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:08.980
did sun automatically mean warm?

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:10.490
Song,

00:13:10.630 --> 00:13:11.530
you're just picking a fight.

00:13:13.320 --> 00:13:13.940
Dong,

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:15.360
when can we get a ride?

00:13:15.390 --> 00:13:16.700
My phone's about to freeze dead.

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:17.940
Boss, I'm not complaining,

00:13:18.150 --> 00:13:18.850
but I've been

00:13:18.910 --> 00:13:20.180
with this company for years,

00:13:20.320 --> 00:13:22.100
and I've only used the company car once.

00:13:22.240 --> 00:13:22.890
I almost forgot

00:13:22.910 --> 00:13:24.250
what it even looks like.

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:27.340
Why don't you walk back yourself?

00:13:27.910 --> 00:13:28.250
Well...

00:13:29.150 --> 00:13:30.130
Give it back to me!

00:13:38.440 --> 00:13:39.250
In this weather,

00:13:39.630 --> 00:13:40.890
aren't they cold in those short socks?

00:13:53.390 --> 00:13:54.580
Fashion and sexy

00:13:54.670 --> 00:13:55.580
keep the cold out.

00:14:07.910 --> 00:14:08.650
Not everyone

00:14:08.670 --> 00:14:09.610
thinks that way.

00:14:37.200 --> 00:14:37.580
Dongshan,

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:38.940
you played great today.

00:14:39.320 --> 00:14:40.250
Was that kick yours?

00:14:40.510 --> 00:14:41.180
Wide-open goal,

00:14:41.440 --> 00:14:42.420
I think Fei could've caught it.

00:14:42.440 --> 00:14:42.890
Right?

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:43.820
We didn't even have enough people.

00:14:43.840 --> 00:14:45.180
I was covering two spots by myself.

00:14:45.550 --> 00:14:46.080
Where's Chi?

00:14:46.080 --> 00:14:46.940
I'll call him and chew him out.

00:14:48.150 --> 00:14:48.770
Chi!

00:14:49.030 --> 00:14:50.060
Over here!

00:14:55.080 --> 00:14:55.820
It can't stop!

00:14:56.080 --> 00:14:57.370
Dongshan, run!

00:15:10.060 --> 00:15:12.460
[Yao "Stinky Foot"]

00:15:26.670 --> 00:15:27.770
Let me pat and comfort you.

00:15:28.320 --> 00:15:28.770
It's okay now.

00:15:30.080 --> 00:15:30.460
Yeah.

00:15:30.630 --> 00:15:31.100
Chi,

00:15:31.600 --> 00:15:32.650
you really need to fix that car.

00:15:32.870 --> 00:15:33.460
Or sooner or later,

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:34.490
you're going to get my uncle killed.

00:15:35.240 --> 00:15:36.010
Hey, Jiang Jialu,

00:15:36.030 --> 00:15:37.420
you really want me dead that bad?

00:15:38.790 --> 00:15:39.980
Today's on me.

00:15:40.030 --> 00:15:40.730
Sooner or later,

00:15:40.750 --> 00:15:41.650
I'll change those brake pads.

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:43.180
Sorry, I scared you.

00:15:43.320 --> 00:15:44.460
Who got scared? I didn't...

00:15:45.150 --> 00:15:45.650
Chi,

00:15:45.670 --> 00:15:46.370
I saw your van

00:15:46.390 --> 00:15:47.420
got a "For Sale" sign on it.

00:15:47.550 --> 00:15:48.130
What's up?

00:15:48.840 --> 00:15:49.980
Yeah, why are you selling it?

00:15:50.030 --> 00:15:51.100
Nothing...

00:15:51.670 --> 00:15:52.180
What are you thinking?

00:15:52.440 --> 00:15:53.730
So what was it today? I missed it.

00:15:53.910 --> 00:15:54.650
Lose? Win?

00:15:54.670 --> 00:15:55.580
Don't ask the score.

00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:56.530
Don't bring it up.

00:15:56.870 --> 00:15:58.370
You weren't there. Jiaqi wasn't there.

00:15:58.670 --> 00:15:59.130
How were we supposed to play?

00:15:59.840 --> 00:16:00.770
It's you. You can't serve!

00:16:00.840 --> 00:16:01.580
You never could!

00:16:01.790 --> 00:16:02.300
Right?

00:16:03.440 --> 00:16:04.220
Now I know

00:16:04.270 --> 00:16:05.010
why you're selling it.

00:16:07.980 --> 00:16:11.340
[For Sale]

00:16:11.360 --> 00:16:11.850
How much did you win?

00:16:13.240 --> 00:16:13.820
What?

00:16:13.910 --> 00:16:14.940
You think I hit the jackpot?

00:16:15.480 --> 00:16:15.980
No.

