[Mr. Liu, E-commerce]

00:19:29.590 --> 00:19:30.240
I'm helping Sen'an

00:19:30.480 --> 00:19:32.460
win the title of Top 10 Innovative Pharma.

00:19:35.550 --> 00:19:36.050
Mr. Gao.

