A single one is enough.

00:21:28.270 --> 00:21:28.980
What do you mean?

00:21:30.720 --> 00:21:31.530
A friend inside the platform

00:21:31.550 --> 00:21:32.380
called me back.

00:21:33.440 --> 00:21:34.140
They said that if we can provide

00:21:34.160 --> 00:21:35.090
one card number,

00:21:35.960 --> 00:21:36.900
they will find out

00:21:37.070 --> 00:21:38.290
who bought those cards.

00:21:43.220 --> 00:21:46.100
[Card No.]

00:21:46.110 --> 00:21:46.730
8906.

00:21:49.070 --> 00:21:50.180
One card ends

00:21:50.200 --> 00:21:51.010
with 8906.

00:21:52.160 --> 00:21:53.010
You're sure you got it right?

